        %div.col-sm-6
          %h1.media-heading{:style=>"margin: 0 0 0 1em;"} eNM ontology viewer
    
    %div.container-fluid
      %topline
        %div.row
          %div.col-md-8
            Problems, bugs, ideas for improvements ? Please report at our
            %a{:href => 'https://github.com/enanomapper/enm-ontoviewer/issues', :rel => "external"} issue tracker
